1
00:00:14,090 --> 00:00:20,390
♪Suddenly, you showed up♪

2
00:00:22,150 --> 00:00:28,750
♪Who stole away those years♪

3
00:00:30,600 --> 00:00:37,320
♪Oh, night and day♪

4
00:00:38,760 --> 00:00:45,540
♪Oh, it's been a long time♪

5
00:00:45,930 --> 00:00:50,050
♪Pass through the bustling world
in the daytime♪

6
00:00:50,050 --> 00:00:53,880
♪Circumvent love at night♪

7
00:00:54,010 --> 00:00:57,760
♪Day after day, year after year♪

8
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:02,040
♪I wake up and close my eyes
before it gets dark♪

9
00:01:02,040 --> 00:01:06,140
♪But when the day breaks into the night♪

10
00:01:06,140 --> 00:01:10,220
♪It makes me believe
that there's still love♪

11
00:01:10,220 --> 00:01:14,050
♪If you want it, if I want it♪

12
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:20,800
♪It's a vow of night and day♪

13
00:01:26,520 --> 00:01:32,890
♪It's a vow of day and night♪

14
00:01:32,890 --> 00:01:37,200
[Blooming]

15
00:01:37,360 --> 00:01:39,920
[Episode 25]

16
00:01:41,800 --> 00:01:44,800
Tantan, I'm really happy

17
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:46,160
that you come back with me.

18
00:01:48,360 --> 00:01:51,640
Then let's collect
the lotus seeds together,

19
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:54,080
liquidate the Demon Lord,
and take revenge for you.

20
00:02:00,240 --> 00:02:02,200
You've traveled all day.

21
00:02:02,320 --> 00:02:03,200
It's time to rest.

22
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:05,560
Prepare two guest rooms,

23
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:07,320
one in the front yard
and one in the back.

24
00:02:07,440 --> 00:02:08,030
Yes.

25
00:02:09,160 --> 00:02:10,360
Stay with me in the front yard.

26
00:02:14,520 --> 00:02:15,080
Well...

27
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:17,200
Cui Chen and I are far apart.

28
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:19,560
We haven't seen each other
for a long time.

29
00:02:19,640 --> 00:02:21,040
Don't you want to talk to me?

30
00:02:21,200 --> 00:02:22,560
I do, but...

31
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:23,240
Tantan.

32
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:26,480
Let's listen to the host.

33
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:29,880
Tomorrow morning,

34
00:02:29,880 --> 00:02:31,440
I'll go ask out about the lotus seed.

35
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:32,600
Don't worry.

36
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:37,320
Let's go.

37
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:05,080
Miss Feng.

38
00:03:05,920 --> 00:03:07,160
I have something to ask you.

39
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:09,440
I have nothing to say to you.

40
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:14,480
We didn't know each other
before the Changluo Town.

41
00:03:15,040 --> 00:03:15,920
Why do you

42
00:03:15,920 --> 00:03:17,520
have such deep prejudice against me?

43
00:03:18,640 --> 00:03:20,880
Heartless people are forgetful indeed.

44
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:22,440
I'm asking you to leave.

45
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:25,640
I haven't finished my question yet.

46
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:29,360
Where did you get
the jade pendant you gave Tantan?

47
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:32,080
Of course it's mine.

48
00:03:33,640 --> 00:03:36,760
Have you seen it somewhere else?

49
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:39,080
My late friend

50
00:03:40,480 --> 00:03:41,920
had a same one.

51
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,320
She treasured it a lot,

52
00:03:44,440 --> 00:03:47,160
and said her best sister also had one,

53
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:49,840
but she never told me her name.

54
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:57,520
Now I know who that person is.

55
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:59,560
Looks like I was careless.

56
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:02,600
Lian Wen did like you a lot back then.

57
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:04,120
She even showed you her jade pendant.

58
00:04:04,200 --> 00:04:05,960
Did you give it to Tantan

59
00:04:06,440 --> 00:04:07,840
because you think she's Lian Wen?

60
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:08,440
Well,

61
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:10,680
if Tantan is Lian Wen,

62
00:04:10,880 --> 00:04:12,480
do you want to kill her again?

63
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:16,600
Feng Bao, what happened back then
was a misunderstanding.

64
00:04:16,760 --> 00:04:17,440
A misunderstanding?

65
00:04:18,390 --> 00:04:19,880
You had the sword,

66
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:22,120
and I saw her die by it.

67
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:23,000
How was it a misunderstanding?

68
00:04:24,080 --> 00:04:25,320
I don't have to explain it to you.

69
00:04:25,520 --> 00:04:28,320
You don't want to or you can't?

70
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:33,680
You brought us to Wanfang City.

71
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:35,240
What's your purpose?

72
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:36,440
What do you think?

73
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:38,120
I don't know what your purpose is.

74
00:04:38,760 --> 00:04:39,760
But I'm warning you,

75
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:41,920
Tantan is Tantan,
and Lian Wen is Lian Wen.

76
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:43,280
She's not a substitute for anyone.

77
00:04:43,280 --> 00:04:44,560
I won't let you hurt her.

78
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,080
How ridiculous.

79
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,360
A heartless hypocrite

80
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:49,920
actually said that to me.

81
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:52,880
Aren't you afraid?

82
00:04:54,960 --> 00:04:55,640
Afraid of what?

83
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:58,160
Afraid that Tantan is Lian Wen,

84
00:04:58,440 --> 00:05:00,120
and she'll remember everything.

85
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:03,720
I'll say it one last time,

86
00:05:04,280 --> 00:05:06,040
what happened back then
was a misunderstanding.

87
00:05:06,400 --> 00:05:07,880
I didn't do anything wrong
to Lian Wen.

88
00:05:22,880 --> 00:05:25,000
Afraid that Tantan is Lian Wen,

89
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:27,120
and she'll remember everything.

90
00:05:35,840 --> 00:05:38,960
(Tantan, if you are Lian her,)

91
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:40,520
(will you hate me?)

92
00:05:41,520 --> 00:05:43,640
(Will you believe the truth I tell you?)

93
00:06:01,880 --> 00:06:03,440
What's wrong? You look mad.

94
00:06:03,640 --> 00:06:04,160
Here.

95
00:06:04,840 --> 00:06:05,520
Have a candy.

96
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:07,440
These are peanut candies
specially prepared for you.

97
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:10,720
Cui Chen said there is a lotus seed
in Wanfang City. Is it true?

98
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:16,840
Looks like you know it.

99
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:18,320
Over these years,

100
00:06:18,960 --> 00:06:20,840
I've been absorbing
the spiritual power of the lotus seed

101
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:22,200
to increase my magic power,

102
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:25,600
so that I could lead the people
to rebuild the city.

103
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:29,360
I've been looking for the lotus seeds
for so many years,

104
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:30,720
but you've been keeping it from me.

105
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:33,520
A hundred years ago,
we saw how scary the Demon Lord was.

106
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:36,600
A single lotus seed can't hurt him.

107
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:39,240
Now the people of Wanfang City

108
00:06:39,640 --> 00:06:40,840
need this lotus seed even more.

109
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:43,080
What about the hatred
of the past hundred years?

110
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:44,440
I'm sorry.

111
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:46,080
As the guardian of the city,

112
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:49,600
my duty is to ensure the safety
of Wanfang City.

113
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:51,280
Fine.

114
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:54,280
Do your job well as a guardian.

115
00:06:54,440 --> 00:06:55,800
Revenge is not your concern.

116
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:58,920
Tell me where the lotus seed is.

117
00:06:59,520 --> 00:07:00,320
I can't tell you.

118
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:01,680
If you won't say,

119
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:03,560
then stay out of my business.

120
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:07,920
Feng Bao, why did you bring
Cui Chen and Zhao Tantan

121
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:08,840
into the city?

122
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:09,920
She's Lian Wen.

123
00:07:10,640 --> 00:07:11,400
Lian When?

124
00:07:14,880 --> 00:07:16,480
She died a hundred years ago.

125
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:17,840
She is Lian Wen.

126
00:07:18,280 --> 00:07:19,400
She just lost her memory.

127
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:21,520
I brought her here this time

128
00:07:22,080 --> 00:07:23,680
to revive her memory,

129
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:26,120
then we can seek revenge together.

130
00:07:28,080 --> 00:07:28,760
Feng Bao.

131
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:31,320
Before Uncle Feng died,

132
00:07:31,960 --> 00:07:33,880
he told you to lead the people
to live a good life.

133
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:35,960
If you keep living in hatred,

134
00:07:36,080 --> 00:07:37,240
you'll be exhausted.

135
00:07:38,280 --> 00:07:40,960
But my father and sister died.

136
00:07:42,320 --> 00:07:44,240
The Demon Lord and Cui Chen
destroyed my life

137
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,640
and my family.

138
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:47,640
I must avenge this.

139
00:07:47,880 --> 00:07:48,720
Cui Chen?

140
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:51,240
He's the one who killed Lian Wen.

141
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:54,400
Cui Chen and Zhao Tantan
are skillful in magic power.

142
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:55,600
You mustn't do anything reckless.

143
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:58,640
Otherwise, you'll not only hurt yourself,

144
00:07:58,760 --> 00:08:01,080
but also bring disaster
to the people of the city.

145
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:06,640
Don't worry, I know what I'm doing.

146
00:08:08,200 --> 00:08:09,640
I only need to keep Cui Chen away,

147
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:12,680
then I can make Tantan
realize she's Lian Wen.

148
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:13,800
How are you going to do it?

149
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:14,800
Stay out of it.

150
00:08:21,520 --> 00:08:24,640
[Feng Mansion]

151
00:08:28,640 --> 00:08:29,640
Miss Tantan.

152
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:31,600
Miss Tantan.

153
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:33,200
Who is it?

154
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,600
It's me, Agua.

155
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:37,280
Lady Feng asked me
to take you to see Uncle Song.

156
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:39,960
Who is Uncle Song?

157
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:41,720
Lady Feng said he's the one here

158
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:43,360
who is most likely to know
where the lotus seed is.

159
00:08:50,160 --> 00:08:51,680
Let's find Cui Chen and leave together.

160
00:08:51,760 --> 00:08:53,760
Lady Feng has sent someone
to inform Mr. Cui.

161
00:08:53,920 --> 00:08:55,520
You can go first.

162
00:08:55,800 --> 00:08:56,400
Okay.

163
00:09:05,800 --> 00:09:06,360
Tantan.

164
00:09:08,880 --> 00:09:09,440
Tantan.

165
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:16,080
Tantan.

166
00:09:20,800 --> 00:09:21,560
Where's Tantan?

167
00:09:22,280 --> 00:09:24,200
Come with me
if you want to know where Tantan is.

168
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:40,520
Uncle Song?

169
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:51,200
Uncle Song?

170
00:10:08,040 --> 00:10:09,480
Are you looking for the lotus seed?

171
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:13,040
Yes.

172
00:10:13,560 --> 00:10:15,400
I heard there's a lotus seed
in Wanfang City.

173
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:17,960
Feng Bao said you're most likely
to know about it.

174
00:10:18,560 --> 00:10:19,400
Choose one.

175
00:10:21,280 --> 00:10:22,280
Choose what?

176
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:23,240
The jade.

177
00:10:24,320 --> 00:10:25,800
I don't like jewelry.

178
00:10:25,800 --> 00:10:26,680
It's for carving.

179
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:28,320
Can I not carve it?

180
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:30,040
That's my rule.

181
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:39,400
I'll choose this one.

182
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:46,480
Tantan is in there.

183
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:48,520
If you want to see her, follow me.

184
00:11:02,680 --> 00:11:04,040
(There is the scent of the lotus seed.)

185
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:08,920
Where's Tantan?

186
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:11,640
I have my plans for her. Don't worry.

187
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:13,440
You should think about

188
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:14,960
how to beg me to let you out.

189
00:11:26,760 --> 00:11:27,320
Well,

190
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:30,800
is the esteemed Mu Bai Zhenren
also scared?

191
00:11:31,880 --> 00:11:33,760
You tricked me into coming here.

192
00:11:33,880 --> 00:11:35,000
What's your purpose?

193
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:40,400
[Spirit Tablet of Lian Wen]

194
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:47,880
Cui Chen, you keep saying

195
00:11:47,880 --> 00:11:49,200
it was a misunderstanding back then.

196
00:11:49,560 --> 00:11:51,360
Do you dare to say in front of Lian Wen

197
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:52,680
that you didn't kill her?

198
00:11:53,880 --> 00:11:54,480
Of course I dare.

199
00:11:55,880 --> 00:11:57,520
I've been an honorable man.

200
00:11:57,680 --> 00:11:58,880
I said I didn't kill Lian Wen.

201
00:11:58,880 --> 00:12:00,040
That means I didn't kill her.

202
00:12:00,120 --> 00:12:02,440
Lian Wen, this is the man you loved.

203
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:04,160
I clearly saw him

204
00:12:04,160 --> 00:12:05,400
plunge his sword into your body,

205
00:12:05,400 --> 00:12:06,640
but now he won't admit it.

206
00:12:06,640 --> 00:12:08,360
Sometimes, what you see may not be true.

207
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:09,320
I used Dongxu Skill...

208
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:09,840
Enough.

209
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:11,440
You just stay here

210
00:12:11,440 --> 00:12:12,840
and explain it to Lian Wen.

211
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:39,800
Polishing jade requires patience.

212
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:42,520
First, rough polishing,

213
00:12:42,920 --> 00:12:45,800
then fine polishing, washing,

214
00:12:46,520 --> 00:12:49,080
and finally applying oil and wax.

215
00:12:50,120 --> 00:12:51,560
Just being a human being.

216
00:12:52,160 --> 00:12:53,560
You need patience

217
00:12:54,040 --> 00:12:57,160
and endurance to achieve great things.

218
00:13:01,040 --> 00:13:02,360
Do you remember?

219
00:13:02,640 --> 00:13:03,640
Remember what??

220
00:13:04,040 --> 00:13:04,920
I'm not carving anymore.

221
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:06,720
Do you know it or not?

222
00:13:06,920 --> 00:13:07,720
I'll leave if you don't know.

223
00:13:11,520 --> 00:13:12,640
What do you want?

224
00:13:19,480 --> 00:13:20,760
Where is the lotus seed?

225
00:13:37,400 --> 00:13:38,400
I didn't know

226
00:13:38,400 --> 00:13:40,120
there are so many secret books
of various sects in Wanfang City.

227
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:45,800
Lian Wen,
what else did you keep from me?

228
00:14:00,080 --> 00:14:01,400
There's something in the jade trowel.

229
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:08,720
The lotus seed's scent
becomes strong suddenly.

230
00:14:09,520 --> 00:14:10,680
It must be here.

231
00:14:31,360 --> 00:14:32,320
It's the lotus seed indeed.

232
00:14:41,800 --> 00:14:43,320
This jade trowel has a spirit.

233
00:14:54,040 --> 00:14:56,480
Are you the Feng Zhai,
the late Lord of Wanfang?

234
00:14:56,760 --> 00:14:57,920
That's me.

235
00:14:58,680 --> 00:14:59,480
Tell me

236
00:14:59,480 --> 00:15:01,240
how you released me.

237
00:15:02,080 --> 00:15:04,600
I used the Qingyuan Sect's
out-of-body power.

238
00:15:05,800 --> 00:15:07,640
I'm Cui Chen of the Qingyuan Sect.

239
00:15:10,440 --> 00:15:13,440
You killed my daughter, my Lian Wen!

240
00:15:14,240 --> 00:15:16,600
Elder Feng, there's a misunderstanding.

241
00:15:16,600 --> 00:15:18,720
There are so many secret books
on magic arts.

242
00:15:18,840 --> 00:15:19,680
You should have heard of

243
00:15:19,800 --> 00:15:21,360
Qingyuan Sect's Dongxu Skill.

244
00:15:33,440 --> 00:15:34,400
You can have it.

245
00:15:40,560 --> 00:15:42,120
Why are you giving this to me?

246
00:15:42,400 --> 00:15:44,200
Besides, jade is fragile.

247
00:15:44,840 --> 00:15:46,440
Can a trowel made of jade be used?

248
00:15:46,760 --> 00:15:48,320
Jade is fragile,

249
00:15:48,600 --> 00:15:50,560
but it can nourish plants and trees.

250
00:16:00,960 --> 00:16:01,760
I'm done carving.

251
00:16:02,120 --> 00:16:04,360
It's been a day,
but it's still not finished.

252
00:16:04,640 --> 00:16:05,800
Go get some rest.

253
00:16:06,400 --> 00:16:08,760
We broke Father's favorite jade trowel.

254
00:16:08,760 --> 00:16:10,360
We should be punished.

255
00:16:10,360 --> 00:16:12,840
I'll buy him ten trowels.

256
00:16:12,960 --> 00:16:14,880
Jade is fragile,

257
00:16:15,320 --> 00:16:17,240
but it can nourish plants and trees.

258
00:16:17,440 --> 00:16:18,600
The purpose of polishing jade

259
00:16:18,720 --> 00:16:21,080
is to refine your characters.

260
00:16:22,320 --> 00:16:23,040
Father.

261
00:16:23,160 --> 00:16:25,760
Why do you have to tend plants
with jade?

262
00:16:25,840 --> 00:16:28,120
Won't it be easily damaged?

263
00:16:28,240 --> 00:16:30,120
I'll get you an iron one.

264
00:16:30,440 --> 00:16:32,160
The more precious something is,

265
00:16:32,400 --> 00:16:34,680
the more careful you should be.

266
00:16:34,800 --> 00:16:37,200
Feng Bao, you're unsettled.

267
00:16:37,520 --> 00:16:40,680
How will you be able to take on the role
of being the leader of Wanfang?

268
00:16:40,720 --> 00:16:41,320
Father.

269
00:16:41,680 --> 00:16:43,120
Feng Bao just wants to make you

270
00:16:43,120 --> 00:16:45,120
a better and stronger trowel.

271
00:16:47,360 --> 00:16:48,240
Feng Bao.

272
00:16:48,680 --> 00:16:49,400
Lian Wen.

273
00:16:50,080 --> 00:16:51,040
They're family.

274
00:16:54,000 --> 00:16:57,440
Lian Wen, are you remembering something?

275
00:17:01,920 --> 00:17:02,680
I'm not Lian Wen.

276
00:17:02,960 --> 00:17:03,960
I'm Zhao Tantan.

277
00:17:04,960 --> 00:17:06,560
The situation was urgent back then.

278
00:17:07,040 --> 00:17:09,320
I wanted to pass my sword
through Lian Wen's body

279
00:17:09,440 --> 00:17:10,870
and kill the assailant behind her,

280
00:17:11,080 --> 00:17:12,000
and then explain to her

281
00:17:12,240 --> 00:17:14,110
that Dongxu Skill
wouldn't hurt her at all.

282
00:17:15,870 --> 00:17:17,350
Maybe it was my hesitation earlier

283
00:17:17,350 --> 00:17:18,480
that made her stop trusting me.

284
00:17:18,840 --> 00:17:19,920
She hated me so much

285
00:17:21,240 --> 00:17:23,110
that she wanted to take revenge on me
with her life.

286
00:17:25,150 --> 00:17:27,520
As spirits, we have our own destiny.

287
00:17:27,920 --> 00:17:30,520
Lian Wen had been a stubborn girl.

288
00:17:30,800 --> 00:17:33,680
No one can stop her
from what she wants to do.

289
00:17:33,840 --> 00:17:36,480
After Wanfang City was destroyed
by the Demon Lord,

290
00:17:36,680 --> 00:17:38,680
the two of them stayed
in this secret chamber

291
00:17:38,800 --> 00:17:41,680
and studied all the secret books
I collected.

292
00:17:42,240 --> 00:17:43,840
Lian Wen learned the Xilan Flower Curse

293
00:17:43,840 --> 00:17:46,160
during that time.

294
00:17:46,360 --> 00:17:49,560
I apologize on behalf of my daughter.

295
00:17:50,760 --> 00:17:51,600
Elder Feng, please rise.

296
00:17:51,920 --> 00:17:54,120
Elder Feng, then how did Lian Wen

297
00:17:54,320 --> 00:17:55,720
get to the Qingyuan Sect?

298
00:17:55,880 --> 00:17:58,520
They found the secret
of the Seven-Leaf Lotus

299
00:17:58,520 --> 00:18:00,920
in one of the books

300
00:18:01,200 --> 00:18:03,640
and wanted to use this divine treasure
of the Qingyuan Sect

301
00:18:03,760 --> 00:18:05,440
to take revenge on the Demon Lord.

302
00:18:09,640 --> 00:18:10,320
Lian Wen.

303
00:18:11,640 --> 00:18:12,760
I'm useless.

304
00:18:12,960 --> 00:18:15,360
Now you have to go to the Qingyuan Sect
to steal the Seven-Leaf Lotus.

305
00:18:16,200 --> 00:18:18,480
Feng Bao, what are you talking about?

306
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:19,920
That's what I should do

307
00:18:19,920 --> 00:18:21,840
for Wanfang City and Father.

308
00:18:22,200 --> 00:18:23,000
Besides,

309
00:18:23,440 --> 00:18:25,120
I'm naturally able
to conceal my demonic aura.

310
00:18:25,520 --> 00:18:27,080
I'm the perfect one
to go to the Qingyuan Sect.

311
00:18:27,600 --> 00:18:28,960
Speaking of that,

312
00:18:29,240 --> 00:18:30,560
you must always remember

313
00:18:30,920 --> 00:18:33,400
not to show your demonic token
when you're out there,

314
00:18:33,600 --> 00:18:35,120
or you'll be in danger.

315
00:18:36,960 --> 00:18:38,080
See,

316
00:18:38,560 --> 00:18:40,200
you revealed yourself
once I mentioned it.

317
00:18:41,320 --> 00:18:42,240
You must remember,

318
00:18:42,720 --> 00:18:44,360
you're different
from the other lotus spirits.

319
00:18:44,480 --> 00:18:47,000
They have five petals,
but you have seven.

320
00:18:47,200 --> 00:18:49,040
That's why you can't be found out.

321
00:18:50,440 --> 00:18:51,320
Okay.

322
00:18:52,240 --> 00:18:53,600
I got nervous when you mentioned it.

323
00:18:53,600 --> 00:18:54,840
And then I revealed it.

324
00:18:55,280 --> 00:18:56,120
Don't worry.

325
00:18:56,720 --> 00:18:58,520
Father taught me
how to hide my demonic token.

326
00:18:58,520 --> 00:18:59,480
I still remember.

327
00:18:59,760 --> 00:19:01,000
If only

328
00:19:01,120 --> 00:19:03,600
they hadn't walked out of here,

329
00:19:03,800 --> 00:19:05,400
Lian Wen wouldn't have died.

330
00:19:08,560 --> 00:19:09,440
Lian Wen!

331
00:19:10,560 --> 00:19:11,360
Lian Wen!

332
00:19:15,800 --> 00:19:17,080
Are you Lian Wen's older sister?

333
00:19:19,120 --> 00:19:21,400
That's right. You finally remembered.

334
00:19:23,240 --> 00:19:24,520
I trusted you so much.

335
00:19:24,840 --> 00:19:26,680
Why did you deceive me?

336
00:19:27,200 --> 00:19:28,520
I'm sorry, Lian Wen.

337
00:19:29,720 --> 00:19:31,440
I wanted to tell you a long time ago,

338
00:19:32,160 --> 00:19:34,440
but you've been rejecting
everything about yourself,

339
00:19:34,560 --> 00:19:36,600
not to mention the fact
that you are Lian Wen.

340
00:19:36,800 --> 00:19:37,320
That's why...

341
00:19:37,320 --> 00:19:38,680
So, you've been so good to me

342
00:19:39,080 --> 00:19:39,960
only because you see me as

343
00:19:39,960 --> 00:19:41,360
Lian Wen's substitute, right?

344
00:19:41,360 --> 00:19:43,160
You've recovered your memories.

345
00:19:43,160 --> 00:19:44,600
Why are you afraid to admit it?

346
00:19:44,600 --> 00:19:46,040
That's not my memory.

347
00:19:46,400 --> 00:19:48,760
It's an illusion
that you made me see with magic.

348
00:19:49,560 --> 00:19:50,440
That's not true.

349
00:19:50,440 --> 00:19:52,920
It's your real memory.

350
00:19:53,960 --> 00:19:55,280
If you don't believe me,

351
00:19:55,640 --> 00:19:57,040
you can look into the Mirror of Truth.

352
00:19:58,760 --> 00:20:00,080
The True Mirror of the Tianyin Palace?

353
00:20:00,320 --> 00:20:00,960
Yes.

354
00:20:01,640 --> 00:20:03,600
It can reveal the demonic token
of all spirits.

355
00:20:09,960 --> 00:20:10,840
Lian Wen.

356
00:20:12,000 --> 00:20:13,480
I'm not Lian Wen,
and I won't look into it.

357
00:20:14,120 --> 00:20:15,160
I'm not a spirit either.

358
00:20:16,480 --> 00:20:18,480
Master never said I'm a spirit.

359
00:20:19,360 --> 00:20:21,160
You have to be brave and face yourself.

360
00:20:22,000 --> 00:20:23,240
You are Lian Wen.

361
00:20:31,840 --> 00:20:34,120
I didn't know
how long they had been gone.

362
00:20:34,120 --> 00:20:36,720
One day, Feng Bao came back and said

363
00:20:36,720 --> 00:20:38,000
that Lian Wen was missing.

364
00:20:38,760 --> 00:20:41,440
She cried in front of me
for three days and nights.

365
00:20:42,120 --> 00:20:44,920
She kept saying that she harmed Lian Wen

366
00:20:45,080 --> 00:20:48,560
and didn't deserve to be her sister.

367
00:20:51,400 --> 00:20:52,040
Elder Feng.

368
00:20:53,920 --> 00:20:55,520
Actually,
on the night before the wedding,

369
00:20:56,000 --> 00:20:57,920
Lian Wen told me she was a spirit.

370
00:20:58,720 --> 00:21:00,200
If I had asked one more question

371
00:21:00,760 --> 00:21:02,440
and known about her heavy past,

372
00:21:03,840 --> 00:21:05,800
maybe all this wouldn't have happened.

373
00:21:07,360 --> 00:21:08,240
Mu Bai.

374
00:21:09,080 --> 00:21:10,440
Will you always trust me?

375
00:21:10,840 --> 00:21:11,800
Why are you asking it?

376
00:21:12,400 --> 00:21:13,120
Nothing.

377
00:21:14,200 --> 00:21:15,600
I just want to know

378
00:21:16,040 --> 00:21:17,400
if you'll always trust me

379
00:21:17,520 --> 00:21:19,000
no matter what happens.

380
00:21:24,240 --> 00:21:26,880
I'll always trust you
no matter what happens.

381
00:21:30,840 --> 00:21:31,440
Mu Bai.

382
00:21:32,640 --> 00:21:33,680
I'm a lotus spirit.

383
00:21:36,160 --> 00:21:36,800
You...

384
00:21:38,000 --> 00:21:38,760
I see.

385
00:21:39,360 --> 00:21:41,280
You can't accept it.

386
00:21:42,920 --> 00:21:44,640
I'll leave the Qingyuan Sect tonight.

387
00:21:50,200 --> 00:21:51,320
I only have one question.

388
00:21:53,880 --> 00:21:55,040
Do you really

389
00:21:56,240 --> 00:21:57,520
want to marry me?

390
00:21:58,880 --> 00:21:59,680
Of course I do.

391
00:22:01,000 --> 00:22:01,840
Then it's good.

392
00:22:02,840 --> 00:22:05,320
Everything else can be solved.

393
00:22:05,880 --> 00:22:06,560
Really?

394
00:22:06,880 --> 00:22:08,120
Really really.

395
00:22:08,880 --> 00:22:10,520
But what happened on the wedding day

396
00:22:10,840 --> 00:22:11,960
was unexpected.

397
00:22:12,640 --> 00:22:14,200
It's also my fault

398
00:22:14,960 --> 00:22:16,000
that it has come to this.

399
00:22:16,640 --> 00:22:17,200
Maybe being locked

400
00:22:17,200 --> 00:22:18,760
in this secret chamber by Feng Bao

401
00:22:19,160 --> 00:22:20,440
is my punishment.

402
00:22:22,280 --> 00:22:24,720
I know about Feng Bao.

403
00:22:25,280 --> 00:22:28,120
Cui Chen, I've lost a daughter.

404
00:22:28,720 --> 00:22:30,640
I don't want to lose Feng Bao.

405
00:22:31,080 --> 00:22:34,040
Consider it compensation for Lian Wen,

406
00:22:34,840 --> 00:22:37,040
can you take me out with you?

407
00:22:38,000 --> 00:22:41,360
Elder Feng, I'm duty-bound to do so,

408
00:22:42,280 --> 00:22:44,040
but I'm also trapped in this chamber.

409
00:22:44,240 --> 00:22:45,280
I can't find a way out either.

410
00:22:45,560 --> 00:22:46,400
Over these years,

411
00:22:46,400 --> 00:22:47,280
you're the only one

412
00:22:47,280 --> 00:22:49,800
who released me from the jade trowel.

413
00:22:50,000 --> 00:22:52,440
And I'm the only one who can save you.

414
00:22:53,320 --> 00:22:57,200
This secret chamber can only be opened
by our family's spell.

415
00:22:57,400 --> 00:22:59,200
But I don't have a physical body.

416
00:22:59,320 --> 00:23:00,760
I can't perform the spell.

417
00:23:01,200 --> 00:23:03,120
I need you to do it for me.

418
00:23:04,000 --> 00:23:05,080
Please tell me what to do.

419
00:23:05,520 --> 00:23:07,800
All you have to do
is to carry me with you.

420
00:23:10,200 --> 00:23:10,840
Elder Feng.

421
00:23:12,080 --> 00:23:12,840
Sorry about this.

422
00:23:30,080 --> 00:23:31,560
Tell the patrol

423
00:23:31,640 --> 00:23:32,720
to check the barrier of the entire city.

424
00:23:32,800 --> 00:23:33,240
Yes.

425
00:23:33,440 --> 00:23:33,920
Let's go.

426
00:23:36,000 --> 00:23:36,800
Cui Chen.

427
00:23:37,400 --> 00:23:39,080
How dare you break into
the Feng Ancestral Hall?

428
00:23:41,000 --> 00:23:42,240
You even stole the lotus seed.

429
00:23:43,160 --> 00:23:44,360
Feng Bao tricked me into going in there.

430
00:23:44,800 --> 00:23:45,600
Feng Bao?

431
00:23:48,200 --> 00:23:48,840
This thing.

432
00:23:49,120 --> 00:23:50,160
You must know what this is.

433
00:23:50,720 --> 00:23:52,320
The late Lord wants to talk to Feng Bao.

434
00:23:52,480 --> 00:23:54,040
Feng Bao's father died
over 100 years ago.

435
00:23:54,360 --> 00:23:55,560
How can he talk to Feng Bao?

436
00:23:56,400 --> 00:23:57,320
I have my own way.

437
00:23:59,280 --> 00:24:00,000
Tantan.

438
00:24:01,080 --> 00:24:02,720
You've been wondering

439
00:24:03,080 --> 00:24:05,200
why you can see Lian Wen in your memory.

440
00:24:05,560 --> 00:24:06,400
The Truth Mirror

441
00:24:06,400 --> 00:24:07,800
can answer this question now.

442
00:24:07,800 --> 00:24:09,080
Why hesitate?

443
00:24:11,200 --> 00:24:12,800
This mirror can only show
the demonic token.

444
00:24:13,120 --> 00:24:13,840
How can it prove

445
00:24:13,840 --> 00:24:15,160
Lian Wen and I are the same person?

446
00:24:15,400 --> 00:24:17,600
The seven-petal lotus flower
on Lian Wen's forehead

447
00:24:17,760 --> 00:24:19,480
is one of a kind.

448
00:24:19,680 --> 00:24:21,400
If you show the same token,

449
00:24:21,720 --> 00:24:23,480
it means you're the same person.

450
00:24:23,760 --> 00:24:24,680
Why are you forcing me

451
00:24:24,680 --> 00:24:26,320
to do something I don't want to do?

452
00:24:26,520 --> 00:24:28,480
Is this your so-called sisterhood?

453
00:24:31,240 --> 00:24:33,600
You want to deny my whole life
with just a mirror

454
00:24:33,960 --> 00:24:34,840
and turn me into someone else.

455
00:24:35,360 --> 00:24:36,440
Don't even think about it.

456
00:24:37,200 --> 00:24:38,440
No matter what,

457
00:24:38,680 --> 00:24:40,280
I'm going to prove that you're Lian Wen.

458
00:24:42,760 --> 00:24:44,800
Xie Yu, why did you let him out?

459
00:24:45,000 --> 00:24:45,800
Miss Feng.

460
00:24:46,040 --> 00:24:46,880
Do you remember this?

461
00:24:47,200 --> 00:24:48,240
How dare you touch my father's relic?

462
00:24:48,240 --> 00:24:49,080
How dare
you disturb the late Lord's soul?

463
00:24:49,080 --> 00:24:49,760
Feng Bao.

464
00:24:50,680 --> 00:24:51,880
Uncle Feng wants to talk to you.

465
00:24:52,240 --> 00:24:53,120
Cui Chen

466
00:24:53,200 --> 00:24:55,240
can release his spirit from the trowel.

467
00:24:55,640 --> 00:24:57,040
How can you believe such nonsense?

468
00:24:57,280 --> 00:24:58,080
You can hold it yourself.

469
00:24:58,600 --> 00:24:59,640
There is nothing to worry about now.

470
00:25:01,480 --> 00:25:02,280
Raise the trowel.

471
00:25:02,720 --> 00:25:04,360
I'll use the Qingyuan Sect's
out-of-body power

472
00:25:04,560 --> 00:25:06,240
and release Elder Feng's spirit.

473
00:25:15,000 --> 00:25:15,760
- My Lord.
- My Lord.

474
00:25:15,800 --> 00:25:16,520
Father.

475
00:25:19,400 --> 00:25:19,960
Father.

476
00:25:20,320 --> 00:25:22,080
Look who she is.

477
00:25:23,200 --> 00:25:24,120
Lian.

478
00:25:24,840 --> 00:25:26,920
Elder Feng, I'm not Lian Wen.

479
00:25:27,360 --> 00:25:28,960
I'm Zhao Tantan of the Qingyuan Sect.

480
00:25:29,600 --> 00:25:30,960
This is our father.

481
00:25:31,120 --> 00:25:32,400
How can you forget that?

482
00:25:39,520 --> 00:25:41,160
The lotus token is too special.

483
00:25:41,320 --> 00:25:43,080
Don't reveal it easily.

484
00:25:45,360 --> 00:25:46,080
Feng Bao.

485
00:25:48,920 --> 00:25:49,680
Lian Wen.

486
00:25:49,960 --> 00:25:51,120
These two jade pendants

487
00:25:51,200 --> 00:25:53,480
will be the symbol of your sisterhood.

488
00:25:53,920 --> 00:25:55,960
From now on, you two
should share everything.

489
00:25:56,120 --> 00:25:59,200
You must love each other
and support each other.

490
00:26:08,400 --> 00:26:08,960
Tantan.

491
00:26:09,760 --> 00:26:11,880
Lian Wen, what else did you see?

492
00:26:12,280 --> 00:26:13,880
Feng Bao, stop pushing her.

493
00:26:14,120 --> 00:26:16,080
You're a murderer.
You have no right to talk.

494
00:26:16,120 --> 00:26:17,080
Feng Bao, stop.

495
00:26:17,280 --> 00:26:18,360
It's been over a hundred years.

496
00:26:18,520 --> 00:26:20,880
You're still so impulsive.

497
00:26:21,000 --> 00:26:23,840
Don't force your will on others.

498
00:26:23,840 --> 00:26:24,680
Father.

499
00:26:25,200 --> 00:26:26,880
How am I forcing her?

500
00:26:28,320 --> 00:26:29,840
She is Lian Wen.

501
00:26:30,240 --> 00:26:31,960
She should bear her responsibilities

502
00:26:32,120 --> 00:26:33,920
and seek revenge
against the Demon Lord with me.

503
00:26:34,280 --> 00:26:35,400
And Cui Chen.

504
00:26:35,960 --> 00:26:38,040
He killed your little daughter.

505
00:26:38,480 --> 00:26:39,720
What's wrong with you?

506
00:26:40,000 --> 00:26:41,280
Are you being threatened?

507
00:26:41,520 --> 00:26:42,920
Why aren't you angry at all?

508
00:26:43,120 --> 00:26:44,040
Feng Bao.

509
00:26:45,480 --> 00:26:48,000
Cui Chen has explained it to me
in the Ancestral Hall.

510
00:26:48,600 --> 00:26:50,920
There was an attacker behind Lian Wen.

511
00:26:51,320 --> 00:26:52,640
In order to save her,

512
00:26:52,760 --> 00:26:54,920
Cui Chen used Dongxu Skill,

513
00:26:55,120 --> 00:26:57,440
passing his sword
through Lian Wen's body,

514
00:26:57,520 --> 00:27:00,520
to hurt the attacker but not her.

515
00:27:00,520 --> 00:27:01,400
Father.

516
00:27:01,920 --> 00:27:04,560
How can you believe such nonsense?

517
00:27:12,040 --> 00:27:13,920
Cui Chen, prove it to us.

518
00:27:14,040 --> 00:27:15,280
I trust you.

519
00:27:19,920 --> 00:27:20,840
Don't worry.

520
00:27:21,200 --> 00:27:22,800
I'm the Light of Qingyuan now.

521
00:27:23,160 --> 00:27:24,440
This won't hurt me.

522
00:27:28,440 --> 00:27:29,320
If you don't do it,

523
00:27:29,400 --> 00:27:30,440
I'll have to do it myself.

524
00:27:30,960 --> 00:27:31,640
No.

525
00:27:46,840 --> 00:27:47,440
Don't!

526
00:27:47,680 --> 00:27:48,440
That's enough.

527
00:27:49,360 --> 00:27:50,840
I don't want to prove anything anymore.

528
00:28:00,080 --> 00:28:01,480
Let's find a place to talk.

529
00:28:02,480 --> 00:28:03,240
Okay.

530
00:28:26,560 --> 00:28:27,320
Dabai.

531
00:28:28,760 --> 00:28:31,960
Who am I in your heart?

532
00:28:33,240 --> 00:28:36,240
In my heart, you're a heroine
of the Xinhuai Village.

533
00:28:36,720 --> 00:28:38,400
You're my junior who caught
the hamster spirit with me.

534
00:28:38,720 --> 00:28:40,240
You're the one who I confessed my love to
in Zhu village.

535
00:28:41,680 --> 00:28:42,760
You're Zhao Tantan,

536
00:28:43,200 --> 00:28:44,720
the one and only Zhao Tantan.

537
00:28:46,080 --> 00:28:46,800
Okay.

538
00:28:47,800 --> 00:28:49,200
Take out the True Mirror.

539
00:28:49,840 --> 00:28:50,720
I want to see

540
00:28:50,880 --> 00:28:52,720
what the relationship is
between me and Lian Wen.

541
00:28:55,480 --> 00:28:56,400
Have you decided?

542
00:28:59,120 --> 00:29:00,000
I've decided.

543
00:29:03,320 --> 00:29:04,240
Well,

544
00:29:04,440 --> 00:29:05,480
even if Lian Wen and I

545
00:29:05,560 --> 00:29:07,400
have the same unique demonic token,

546
00:29:08,120 --> 00:29:10,000
she's still my past life.

547
00:29:10,520 --> 00:29:11,960
Based on your descriptions

548
00:29:12,160 --> 00:29:13,880
and my sporadic memories,

549
00:29:14,000 --> 00:29:15,920
we are different people.

550
00:29:17,520 --> 00:29:19,240
I don't care about her past.

551
00:29:19,800 --> 00:29:22,560
What I care about is our present.

552
00:29:31,680 --> 00:29:33,240
You forgot to keep your distance again.

553
00:29:37,040 --> 00:29:38,040
Take it out.

554
00:29:38,840 --> 00:29:41,240
I'll look into it
and give an explanation to others.

555
00:29:44,040 --> 00:29:44,760
Okay.

556
00:30:18,440 --> 00:30:20,200
It's just as I thought.

557
00:30:21,000 --> 00:30:22,400
But it still feels incredible

558
00:30:23,320 --> 00:30:25,040
when I see it myself.

559
00:30:26,600 --> 00:30:27,240
Tantan.

560
00:30:28,440 --> 00:30:29,640
I'm fine.

561
00:30:31,520 --> 00:30:32,960
I'm just a little emotional.

562
00:30:34,320 --> 00:30:36,520
I never expected someone
who passed away over 100 years ago

563
00:30:37,200 --> 00:30:39,080
to have such a connection with me.

564
00:30:45,720 --> 00:30:46,920
Let's talk about something happy.

565
00:30:47,720 --> 00:30:49,840
By the way, I have good news for you.

566
00:30:53,920 --> 00:30:54,640
Look.

567
00:30:59,280 --> 00:31:00,320
A lotus seed?

568
00:31:00,680 --> 00:31:01,920
Where did you find it?

569
00:31:02,200 --> 00:31:03,440
In the Ancestral Hall of Wanfang City.

570
00:31:04,600 --> 00:31:05,080
Well,

571
00:31:05,520 --> 00:31:07,120
is this what they call

572
00:31:07,840 --> 00:31:09,920
"Misfortune may be a blessing
in disguise"?

573
00:31:10,840 --> 00:31:11,720
Well done.

574
00:31:11,920 --> 00:31:13,200
You're getting more knowledgeable.

575
00:31:13,320 --> 00:31:14,840
Master would be very happy to know that.

576
00:31:16,880 --> 00:31:17,840
Touch it.

577
00:31:18,560 --> 00:31:19,640
After you touch the lotus seed,

578
00:31:20,040 --> 00:31:20,800
you'll be able

579
00:31:20,800 --> 00:31:22,720
to reach the Divinity Phase.

580
00:31:24,280 --> 00:31:25,200
Really?

581
00:31:26,640 --> 00:31:28,280
If I touch two more,

582
00:31:28,400 --> 00:31:29,480
will I be able

583
00:31:29,960 --> 00:31:31,400
to reach the highest level
in the Qingyuan Sect,

584
00:31:31,520 --> 00:31:33,360
Dacheng Skill, just like you did?

585
00:31:34,160 --> 00:31:34,840
Maybe.

586
00:31:38,720 --> 00:31:39,960
Who do you think you are?

587
00:31:40,240 --> 00:31:42,040
You won't have a future together.

588
00:31:51,600 --> 00:31:52,480
What happened?

589
00:31:53,200 --> 00:31:54,320
What did you see?

590
00:31:55,640 --> 00:31:56,560
I...

591
00:31:57,120 --> 00:31:58,720
I just saw

592
00:31:58,800 --> 00:32:00,400
some memories of the massacre,

593
00:32:00,720 --> 00:32:01,960
and it scared me a bit.

594
00:32:02,680 --> 00:32:03,600
Really?

595
00:32:05,480 --> 00:32:06,280
Really.

596
00:32:06,480 --> 00:32:07,600
Don't worry.

597
00:32:08,080 --> 00:32:10,760
I'm now a high-ranking cultivator
of the Qingyuan Sect.

598
00:32:11,560 --> 00:32:12,800
I won't be scared easily.

599
00:32:15,560 --> 00:32:16,280
Tantan.

600
00:32:17,480 --> 00:32:19,320
No matter what scary memories
you see next time,

601
00:32:19,680 --> 00:32:21,840
you can tell me right away.
I'll be there for you.

602
00:32:24,400 --> 00:32:25,040
Okay.

603
00:32:25,520 --> 00:32:26,760
Let's go find Feng Bao now

604
00:32:27,040 --> 00:32:28,520
and tell her the result
of the Truth Mirror.

605
00:32:41,840 --> 00:32:43,920
Father, rest assured.

606
00:32:44,400 --> 00:32:46,600
I'll avenge your death
and Lian Wen's death.

607
00:32:52,000 --> 00:32:56,560
Bao, it's time to let go of the hatred.

608
00:32:57,200 --> 00:33:00,680
The people of Wanfang City
are waiting for you to grow up.

609
00:33:04,760 --> 00:33:06,800
Father, I'm sorry.

610
00:33:08,080 --> 00:33:10,000
I failed to fulfill your instructions.

611
00:33:10,920 --> 00:33:12,920
I didn't guard Wanfang City well.

612
00:33:14,000 --> 00:33:16,960
I've been wandering around
all these years,

613
00:33:17,080 --> 00:33:18,720
looking for a chance to take revenge,

614
00:33:19,800 --> 00:33:22,880
but I forgot
my most important responsibility.

615
00:33:23,240 --> 00:33:26,680
Good girl, you're doing well now.

616
00:33:26,960 --> 00:33:29,480
Besides, I have a son-in-law.

617
00:33:30,640 --> 00:33:32,920
You two can join hands

618
00:33:33,000 --> 00:33:34,960
to protect our people.

619
00:33:35,600 --> 00:33:37,240
Father, what are you talking about?

620
00:33:37,400 --> 00:33:38,760
We're not married yet.

621
00:33:38,960 --> 00:33:41,040
Then keep an eye on him.

622
00:33:41,120 --> 00:33:43,000
Don't let anyone steal him.

623
00:33:43,440 --> 00:33:45,440
Or you'll come back
to the secret chamber

624
00:33:45,560 --> 00:33:46,600
and cry in front of my tablet.

625
00:33:46,720 --> 00:33:48,240
I can't stand that.

626
00:33:48,480 --> 00:33:51,840
Father, why the tablet?

627
00:33:53,200 --> 00:33:55,240
Can't Cui Chen make you stay forever?

628
00:33:55,480 --> 00:33:59,160
Silly girl, this is just my spirit.

629
00:33:59,400 --> 00:34:01,120
I have to leave.

630
00:34:01,600 --> 00:34:04,040
Father, don't leave.

631
00:34:04,360 --> 00:34:06,600
I've been missing you
for over 100 years.

632
00:34:08,920 --> 00:34:09,400
My Lord.

633
00:34:09,400 --> 00:34:11,080
Cui Chen, do something.

634
00:34:11,200 --> 00:34:12,200
Make my father stay.

635
00:34:12,200 --> 00:34:13,200
He can't go.

636
00:34:13,400 --> 00:34:14,710
Brother, save my father.

637
00:34:14,790 --> 00:34:15,790
Save him.

638
00:34:16,000 --> 00:34:17,080
The power of the Qingyuan Sect

639
00:34:17,440 --> 00:34:19,270
can only summon Elder Feng's spirit.

640
00:34:19,880 --> 00:34:21,840
Now his spirit is dissipating.

641
00:34:22,000 --> 00:34:24,270
I heard you call me father again.

642
00:34:24,560 --> 00:34:26,310
That's enough for me.

643
00:34:27,000 --> 00:34:28,360
When you miss me in the future,

644
00:34:28,560 --> 00:34:30,400
just look at the sky of Wanfang City.

645
00:34:30,790 --> 00:34:34,200
I'll be protecting you from above,

646
00:34:34,440 --> 00:34:36,310
and protecting Wanfang City.

647
00:34:38,000 --> 00:34:40,520
Don't leave, please.

648
00:34:42,480 --> 00:34:43,440
Father.

